datasets.name: dataset_14
queryLines: SELECT Home_Tile AS Home_Tile, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Tile_Views) AS Total_Unique_Tile_Views, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Tile_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Tile_Clicks, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Interstitial_Views) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Views, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Interstitial_Primary_Button_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Primary_Button_Clicks, MEASURE(Total_Unique_Interstitial_Secondary_Button_Clicks) AS Total_Unique_Interstitial_Secondary_Button_Clicks, MEASURE(f_ctr) AS Percent_Home_Tile_Clicked_vs_Homepage_Displayed, MEASURE(f_ctr_cta_primary) AS Percent_Primary_Button_Clicked_vs_Tile_Displayed, MEASURE(f_ctr_primary) AS Percent_Primary_Button_Clicked_vs_Interstitial_Tile_Displayed, MEASURE(f_ctr_secondary) AS Percent_Secondary_Button_Clicked_vs_Interstitial_Tile_Displayed, MEASURE(Percent_Secondary_Button_Clicked_vs_Tile_Displayed) AS Percent_Secondary_Button_Clicked_vs_Tile_Displayed FROM hpx_events_model_homepage_summary GROUP BY Home_Tile ORDER BY Percent_Secondary_Button_Clicked_vs_Tile_Displayed DESC
